omerates  nyse mkt  back  view original format copyright  public technologies inc  privacy policy  terms of use  contact lgl group inc lgl company profile  reuterscom x edition united states africa américa latina عربي argentina brasil canada  deutschland españa france india italia  méxico россия united kingdom united states profile lgl group inc lgl related topics stocksstock screenerindustrialselectrical components  equipment overview news key developments people charts financials analysts research pulse lgl on american stock exchange usd  aug  change  chg   prev close  open  days high  days low  volume  avg vol  wk high  wk low  full description the lgl group inc incorporated on july   is a holding company the company operates through its subsidiary mtron industries inc which includes the operations of piezo technology inc and mtron asia llc collectively mtronpti the company operates through electronic components segment which includes all products manufactured and sold by mtronpti mtronpti designs markets and manufactures frequency and spectrum control products these componentlevel devices are used in infrastructure equipment for the telecommunications and network equipment industries as well as in electronic systems for applications in defense aerospace earthorbiting satellites downhole drilling medical devices instrumentation industrial devices and global positioning systemsmtronptis portfolio is divided into two product groupings frequency control and spectrum control mtronptis frequency control product group includes a portfolio of clock oscillators voltagecontrolled crystal oscillator vcxo temperature compensated crystal oscillator tcxo ovencontrolled crystal oscillator ocxo and double oven controlled quartz crystal oscillators docxo devices these products are designed for applications within aerospace and defense telecommunications infrastructure and instrumentation marketsmtronptis spectrum control product group includes a range of radio frequency rf microwave and millimeter wave filters and diplexers covering a frequency range from  megahertz mhz to  gigahertz ghz and solid state power amplifiers covering a frequency range from  mhz to  ghz with power output from  watts to  kilowatts filter devices include crystal ceramic tubular combline cavity interdigital and metal insert waveguide as well as digital analog and mechanical tunable filters switched filter arrays and rf subsystems power amplifiers add active devices to mtronptis portfolio and include gallium nitride gan gallium arsenide fieldeffect transistor gaasfet laterally diffused metal oxide semiconductor ldmos and chip and wire technologies in narrow or broadband module or rackmounted packages these products are employed in applications within the aerospace defense and commercial marketsthe company competes with knowles corporation dover corporation cts corporation and rakon limited » full overview of lgl company address lgl group inc  shader rdorlando   fl    p f  company web links home page officers  directors name compensation michael ferrantino  mario gabelli  patti smith  robert mamazza  timothy foufas  » more officers  directors lgl group inc news brieflgl group reports q earnings per share  may   brieflgl group q eps  mar   » more lgl news related topics stocksstock screenerindustrialselectrical components  equipment lgl group   email us subscribe   home about ushistory management board of directors operationsptf mtronpti investorsinvestor relations sec filings annual reports financial highlights press roompress releases sec filings contact   american stock exchange ase symbol lgl   last    date    time am   change    open    high    low    volume    prev close    bid    ask    eps    year low    year high  the lgl group inc announces plans for rights offering to stockholdersdownload the lgl group inc reports q  financial resultsdownload the lgl group inc reports full year and q  financial resultsdownload the lgl group inc reports third quarter  financ