na based in orlando florida with manufacturing in the united states and india mtronpti is vertically integrated with deep experience in basic material science design and manufacturing with as rev c and iso  certification sales and support worldwide and as a recognized service leader mtronpti supports innovation and reliability at major oems including cisco raytheon ericsson harris rockwell collins utc aerospace and nearly  smaller clients through distribution partners learn more…     annual report market watch stay up to date lgl group copyright  all rights reserved   shader road orlando fl  phone   lgl group inc lgl key developments  reuterscom x edition united states africa américa latina عربي argentina brasil canada  deutschland españa france india italia  méxico россия united kingdom united states lgl group inc lgl related topics stocksstock screenermarket dataindustrialselectrical components  equipment overview news key developments people charts financials analysts research pulse lgl on american stock exchange usd  aug  change  chg   prev close  open  days high  days low  volume  avg vol  wk high  wk low  latest key developments source significant developments lgl group reports q earnings per share  thursday  may  am edt  may  reuters  lgl group inc the lgl group inc reports q  financial resultsq earnings per share q revenue rose  percent to  millionorder backlog improved  to  million at march   from  million at march    full article lgl group q eps  tuesday  mar  am edt  lgl group inc  the lgl group inc reports full year and q  financial results  q earnings per share   q revenue rose  percent to  million order backlog improved  to  million at december   from  million at december    full article lgl group q revenue  mln thursday  nov  pm est  lgl group inc  lgl group inc says order backlog improved  to  million at september   from  million at june    lgl group reports third quarter  financial results  q earnings per share  q revenue rose  percent to  million  